{"tid":214592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當你屙完屎發現無廁紙，你會點？","createTime":"2017-04-23T21:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T14:48:13.000Z","uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"766aea0ea1c77e8499784b5660ec43a3dd54ab75","tid":214592,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T21:57:30.000Z","msg":"交代返背景<br />\n我琴日返咗大陸行下街食下野<br />\n行行吓商場嗰陣好急屎<br />\n好啦諗住搵廁所解決 點知個廁所係4樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而殘廁就係我面前<br />\n屌咁我梗係乜都唔理 屙左先講啦<br />\n我又怕大陸啲廁所板污糟但我又好撚急<br />\n於是將啲紙巾鋪左係廁所板上邊<br />\n我屙完先知道淨返一格廁紙 <br />\n係一格 係一格啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想伸手過隔離都無得伸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身上得返幾張紙幣<br />\n我猶豫左一陣諗緊到底好唔好攞嚟炆屎<br />\n結果都係用咗嗰幾張紙幣黎炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n無電話 乜柒都放左係個朋友度<br />\n好彩仲有褲袋嗰幾張紙幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ea405f03eaedfc5f2d5acfe273704c7d7496c3","tid":214592,"uid":29448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:07:25.000Z","msg":"用襪"},{"pid":"d311f91b9b2291dd115ad26f07ee1991a5a3c02e","tid":214592,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:08:07.000Z","msg":"唯有用手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef11c43fbe1bc541b16e2093ec09104cd94b158","tid":214592,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用襪</blockquote><br />\n我着白襪啊 可唔可以放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049f3221745611e2c583d4fefeaa003e202e81fd","tid":214592,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唯有用手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真有諗過 但我過唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63032c1251a18e1548a306b2523482b3bca2777e","tid":214592,"uid":67127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用襪</blockquote><br />\n我着白襪啊 可唔可以放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用完掉落垃圾桶"},{"pid":"5498e9686d0c2173f6b78c5e124b8cd7f7ce5b12","tid":214592,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:20:38.000Z","msg":"唔炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbc45d0045ae4de64c1b1ae0110493b6658e5f2","tid":214592,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有成日流流長真係頂唔住喎師傅"},{"pid":"348a1e74ca843c86084adc00ce058b88a5745cdf","tid":214592,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔炆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有成日流流長真係頂唔住喎師傅</blockquote><br />\n搵人奶番乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856bb94582e554f268e749bd34587d080047bf11","tid":214592,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:41:30.000Z","msg":"你拎返舖係面個啲咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070f0ada8e32899b2ef2829ec494fa1123592bda","tid":214592,"uid":86754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你拎返舖係面個啲咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係已經跌晒落去"},{"pid":"d5b95fc042657a1ff21dab6bf2f703809cbd03f5","tid":214592,"uid":61766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"人仔肯肯定污糟過塊廁板"}]}